{"tid":843165,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【港姐老公兩大摯愛】「小巨B」未識跑「小巨人」勢率先衝線","createTime":"2018-10-01T03:03:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T03:07:23.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6ec3171506b2e88ce536ab414b1054a1bae9b5f3","tid":843165,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:03:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180929/large/1538203170_d38f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180929%2Flarge%2F1538203170_d38f.jpg&h=32c66b1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n賀賢一家三口<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180929/large/1538194467_2369.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180929%2Flarge%2F1538194467_2369.jpg&h=433bbeea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n賀賢花了很多心機照顧三戰兩勝的小巨人（7號）<br />\n<br />\n賀賢太太、2009年港姐亞軍李姿敏，於七月時誕下8.3磅男B賀朗琋(Hunter Hall)，賀賢身為好爸爸，當然被小巨B收服，錫到佢燶。在馬房內賀賢亦有「小巨人」，同樣對牠愛護有加。<br />\n<br />\n「小巨人」雖已6歲，但在港只3戰，自從上年十月中勝出後，已差不多一年未出過賽，今次牠復出跑國慶賽馬日（10月1日）第10場二班田草1200米，賀賢確實花了不少心機和時間。馬會官方傷患紀錄，就指牠左前腿不良於行，賀賢對此作出闡釋。<br />\n<br />\n「『小巨人』在港出賽三次得兩冠一季，上名率100%，反映牠的質素一定甚佳，可惜其蹄甲經常爆裂，難以接受操練。因此自上季贏馬後，已約有一年未出賽，不過唞暑後其情況有改善，今季可勤做快跳工夫，更且更試了三課大閘才跑，當然對提升狀態大有幫助。」<br />\n<br />\n「今場『小巨人』排得二檔起步好跑，由潘頓操刀，對發揮必有幫助，現時只考慮牠缺陣太久，首戰能否重拾競賽意識，這是我有點擔心的，但牠的實力深不可測，若然可發揮出應水準，當有取勝機會。」賀賢說。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/racing/realtime/article/20180930/58737591\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fracing%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180930%2F58737591&d=IY9ik%2BbGM%2BtiGt2nohrInhxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=bc9f4f4d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fracing%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180930%2F58737591&h=718d25f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/racing/realtime/article/20180930/58737591</a>"},{"pid":"94879087d1f72cacae4bdc1cf4e86c41bd66a662","tid":843165,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:07:23.000Z","msg":"鬼唔望墮馬死撚左去 咁樣折磨隻馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}